Package: simpriord
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Prior Data
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Mackson Ncube
Maintainer: Mackson Ncube <macksonncube.stats@gmail.com>
Description: Package to explore how data used as prior information influences
    parameter estimates from Bayesian models.  The package includes functions to 
    streamline simulating data sets and running brms models.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
